Chordate:



Chordate heard some noise behind him, and due to one cloaked intruder, he was 
ready to pull out his heavy laser rifle.  Turning his chair around to face 
the maker of the noises, he smiled at seeing who it was.

"Feline!" he said, getting up and calmly walking over to her.  "Just in time. 
 We may be able to go for that walk after all, kitty cat, an---oh, hey, were 
you lost?"
